results.description:
Hi Agile Coaches! 

Let's start our first meet up in a rather small group to get to know each other and bring in some topics and questions from our practices. The suggested program: 

1. Welcome and introduction 

2. A short discussion about this community meet up and a community manifesto. 

3. Lean coffee session about Agile Coaching 

4. Feedback 

The meeting room, coffee and thee is arranged for 10 euro's per persoon. Please pay cash at the start of the meeting. Let's have a great agile quality time and meet up! Cheers, Akbar
results.name: First Agile Coaching The Hague Meet Up Session

results.description:
Hi Agile Coaches! 

Please welcome to join the monthly meet up every last Thursday of the month. Our next session will be on the following topics: 

1) Exchanging idea's and experiences about Retrospectives. 

2) Short break 

3) An agile coffee session to discuss different questions and topics attendees like to bring in. 

4) Voting on the theme for next meet up 

5) Feedback 

To keep the costs low, a nice meeting room + flipover in the beautiful building of Haagsche Toren (the highest building in The Hague) has been arranged for 10 euro's per persoon. 

Please pay cash at the start of the meeting. 

It is possible to have drinks at the bar (ground floor) or at the sky bar on (41th floor) on your own account. 

Let's have a great agile quality time and meet up! 

Cheers, Akbar
results.name: Monthly Agile Coaching The Hague Meet Up
